{"tid":1626712,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"點解一定要聚埋一齊，點解唔繼續遍地開花","createTime":"2019-10-05T12:38:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:53:58.000Z","uid":222614,"like":13,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"919c3fc4f05f7c0390539e34a2e4376c90447542","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係咁叫人10月6聚係一處遊行<br />\n<br />\n就算畀你叫到700萬人塞爆港島或九龍又點？<br />\n政府有理過香港人咩？<br />\n<br />\n你地係咪覺得連日黎既遍地開花好撚失敗？<br />\n<br />\n點解一定要全部人聚埋一齊？<br />\n<br />\n點解唔繼續遍地開花？<br />\n<br />\n你地究竟想點</span>"},{"pid":"b45ed54638f1643ef669cc214908b798384eb012","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:39:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">快閃行動，遍地開花</span>"},{"pid":"4f2681eb8b8753d5d0cc6f98105b826595fc0b29","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:40:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民陣我屌你老母呀</span>"},{"pid":"efeee87c1b0409a8210bf179d1460042173bdb44","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民我屌你老母呀</span>"},{"pid":"db3adc9e9291d9d11e66a0a3f6129ed41187c7d4","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:41:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠仆街含家產</span>"},{"pid":"09d882500126818011eb405607e7ca3cbedf16f8","tid":1626712,"uid":13936,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:42:37.000Z","msg":"分化  BLOCKED"},{"pid":"5cd784bde869a99a3a3dae2daf46ea57825215c5","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:42:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">答我呀你班仆街，係咁吹雞，理據呢？</span>"},{"pid":"162c9def12b40a6c3b11b149cae08b1f70e02ce9","tid":1626712,"uid":57868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"做俾美國睇啊"},{"pid":"a704cb2200c66042ad63aaa1bddacd12dd8695e4","tid":1626712,"uid":219265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:44:19.000Z","msg":"無錯<br />\n唔好再拎個遊行人數打飛機<br />\n依家個政府擺到明就係唔理你有幾多人<br />\n而且你遊行又做唔到乜野<br />\n只會引晒所有人喺同一個地方<br />\n危害左大家嘅安全"},{"pid":"d32abdc4468c74017ba5eb9e87c2e476f07cdf5b","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民做唔到大台，就係背後搞埋啲咁既小動作，你老味</span>"},{"pid":"4bc2a6b575c88445d0bae95bc04b015e177d9dd7","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162c9def12b40a6c3b11b149cae08b1f70e02ce9","tid":1626712,"uid":57868,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:43:19.000Z","msg":"做俾美國睇啊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">18區遍地開花全世界睇到曬呀</span>"},{"pid":"26e44ff2d20c6cd45f8e80d81ae26596ab78ef86","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:46:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾泛民到今日都仍然想過大佬癮</span>"},{"pid":"074ac86ddbd6095afecdb0e071f17b9d57ff751a","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:47:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民陣我屌你老母，入黎解釋呀</span>"},{"pid":"4b588a67772a76f2562b432b64414d8fb81c6ccb","tid":1626712,"uid":93451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:49:10.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果學校範圍唔算公眾地方 <br />\n聽日一齊返學校有無得諗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我相信好多人都認為聽日係和理非回合[url][/url]<br />\n想出去表達 打下條國際線<br />\n但揾唔到一個一開始同最後唔比人清場嘅方法<br />\n但如果我地帶口罩係大學<br />\n校友\b,大學生,中學生 仲有唔同年齡愛香港嘅香港人<br />\n一齊進行學術討論討論下香港又得唔得呢？<br />\n<br />\n純粹諗到想討論下可行性<br />\n可能時間係好趕<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但聽日最緊要係做到野 同安全</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n我地好耐無新嘅創意啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果八大有好多香港人坐晒係到<br />\n帶口罩表達自己意見<br />\n我覺得個畫面會同二百萬人一樣咁好睇</span></span></strong></span><br />\n最好有法律巴絲入黎分析下<br />\n一齊入黎討論下<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1626652/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1626652/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"7591b98c37c7747e4407bb8b0b06a17d6c2650a2","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:51:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民唔撚係以為03年對付老董個招今日仲有效咩？<br />\n<br />\n泛民成班垃圾智將</span>"},{"pid":"8507eb9a48b4d7c4bd0234bdfce89ec5423fa680","tid":1626712,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c9b493ea730297c7170b8ba85a4ceaf97c454b24","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:56:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">講你地個plan 黎聽下啦喂<br />\n<br />\n300 萬人塞爆港島或九龍，跟住呢？<br />\n<br />\n泛民有成個plan 說服到我既，聽日我個小組就聽你指揮</span>"},{"pid":"05c798da729426b74e65e69f79084c76e0d44067","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8507eb9a48b4d7c4bd0234bdfce89ec5423fa680","tid":1626712,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請問智將，唔通300 百萬人塞死一個地方就無你以上所講既問題？</span>"},{"pid":"a7699a1e389cca004aed53d194e9128f1fe180bb","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:08:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民左膠我屌你老母，亡我革命之心不死<br />\n<br />\n雨傘畀你成功左，但呢場革命你唔洗旨意</span>"},{"pid":"68f2d395f1215ba912e87000734fece7321b9acb","tid":1626712,"uid":106929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05c798da729426b74e65e69f79084c76e0d44067","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8507eb9a48b4d7c4bd0234bdfce89ec5423fa680","tid":1626712,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T12:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請問智將，唔通300 百萬人塞死一個地方就無你以上所講既問題？</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:08:41.000Z","msg":"人少 ，大家叫完口號 ，唱完歌<br />\n做晒和理非想做既野 ，就起行<br />\n攪完 黑警先岩岩上完裝 來攪清楚位置<br />\n都散水<br />\n<br />\n幾十萬人出來 ，攪兩攪又遲到 又拖延<br />\n人又多 到有行動 黑警都準備好晒"},{"pid":"d5ee7d9b0d0bd9f6ec7b0f9472b1e5be4d38a823","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:20:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">垃圾民陣，淨識搞遊行搞音響<br />\n<br />\n洗親都幾十萬去做埋啲低效能既野<br />\n<br />\n不如你地學下去組織一場快閃行動啦，唔洗幾十萬咖<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"7a423b9433edc9db015d93027b8ed3d84a5f487e","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:26:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">泛民知唔知咩叫勢如破竹呀？<br />\n<br />\n你地睇下十月一到依家幾咁成功<br />\n<br />\n但你地就一直想破壞佢，我明，因為功勞唔係你地度！</span>"},{"pid":"96f258abe01de20c28ca5d9cf0c94bdab3e0c52a","tid":1626712,"uid":261478,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"聽曰港島記住係和平遊行<br />\n盡量吸多D和理非出黎<br />\n和理非唔好怕無不反對通知書<br />\n香港已經唔講法律<br />\n有不反對通知書都照拉鳩你架啦<br />\n所以聽日為香港全世界出黎港島<br />\n勇和一家目標300萬人和平遊行<br />\n畀人知道香港人係和平嘅<br />\n暴力嘅係政府<br />\n要吸多D國際支持<br />\n<br />\n同時我唔反對衝衝子去衝<br />\n但記住要散水返左屋企先<br />\n避免畀狗圍無路走唔到<br />\n返左屋企之後再係屋企步行範圍內快閃游擊<br />\n拆鐵拆政府建築幫中資國企裝修<br />\n裝修到星期二開唔到門就變相三罷<br />\n唔好等有狗出現就要散水轉場<br />\n記住我地優勢係人多機動性高<br />\n攰同餓就返屋企食飯休息回滿升先再第日出過<br />\n有唔對路就返屋企訓覺唔好送頭<br />\n<br />\n幫手推POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1626523/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1626523/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"2963c7de65236808e9f701c546e9bfba40597664","tid":1626712,"uid":329257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"塞爆一個地方唔係俾政府睇 係俾國際睇"},{"pid":"ce6782e4f5ca0947177cb7fa076549106c6331f3","tid":1626712,"uid":222614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2963c7de65236808e9f701c546e9bfba40597664","tid":1626712,"uid":329257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:35:39.000Z","msg":"塞爆一個地方唔係俾政府睇 係俾國際睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:36:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">18區遍地開花全世界睇到曬呀</span>"}]}